#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:2 640f515162574b1a9c98187569141306
msgid "Fine-Tuning FAQ"
msgstr "微调常见问题"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:6 1480039684f04e7bab8e83a946dea6d5
msgid "General"
msgstr "通用"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:8 68274fd5be6243299c20e3931d7cbcd3
msgid "**Can I fine-tune for a new language?**"
msgstr "**可以为新语言做微调吗？**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:10 b6cc21ffb2634911bf8eeb2d3ee064e3
msgid ""
"Yes. For languages not yet supported by VoxCPM, we recommend full fine-"
"tuning with 500+ hours of target-language data, mixed with some "
"Chinese/English data to reduce forgetting. Use conservative learning rates "
"(``1e-5``). For the full workflow, see :doc:`./finetune`."
msgstr ""
"可以。对 VoxCPM 尚未覆盖的语言，建议使用目标语言 500+ "
"小时数据做全量微调，并混入部分中英数据以减轻遗忘。学习率宜保守（``1e-5``）。完整流程见 :doc:`./finetune`。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:14 8c642b7875f244cf94269a296884fe2c
msgid "Training Issues"
msgstr "训练问题"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:16 b69d1c7a683e47e692ff83c93707482b
msgid "**Out of memory (OOM):**"
msgstr "**显存不足（OOM）：**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:18 466fa88ba67e49baa407f1abe2622f6f
msgid ""
"Reduce ``batch_size`` or ``max_batch_tokens`` to filter out long samples."
msgstr "降低 ``batch_size`` 或 `` max_batch_tokens``，以过滤掉过长样本。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:19 9f1303be80324494b5e2639802a20a6b
msgid ""
"Increase ``grad_accum_steps`` to maintain effective batch size with less "
"per-step memory."
msgstr "增大 ``grad_accum_steps``，在降低单步显存的同时保持等效 batch。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:20 4cd6e54402e84f079ed05a15adccc152
msgid ""
"Switch to LoRA fine-tuning — it uses roughly half the VRAM of full fine-"
"tuning."
msgstr "改用 LoRA 微调 — 显存占用约为全量微调的一半。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:21 beb233677d65499b8034418840092f80
msgid ""
"For multi-GPU (DDP), expect ~10 GB additional VRAM per card from gradient "
"buckets and NCCL buffers."
msgstr "多卡 DDP 时，梯度桶与 NCCL 缓冲通常每张卡额外需要约 10 GB 显存。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:23 e962d230939e4741b3392e0bc7f15fed
msgid "**Training loss not converging:**"
msgstr "**训练损失不收敛：**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:25 85d3f2669c2e4e26a3de9d48beda1dfc
msgid "Decrease ``learning_rate``."
msgstr "降低 ``learning_rate``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:26 d751696ac840437290fe837c71dddb03
msgid "Increase ``warmup_steps``."
msgstr "增大 ``warmup_steps``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:27 ea34e88bddb5465db72bf06d42327b0c
msgid ""
"Check data quality — noisy audio or mismatched transcripts are common "
"culprits."
msgstr "检查数据质量 — 噪声音频或转写不匹配是常见原因。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:29 242eef87a77b45e3a883e571193e6456
msgid ""
"**Resume training shows wrong step count:** (`#187 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/187>`_)"
msgstr ""
"**恢复训练后步数显示异常：** （`#187 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/187>`_）"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:32 1f4ddd73935940c4917fc02ee5a4c5e7
msgid ""
"This is a known bug in multi-GPU training. Ensure you are using the latest "
"version of the training scripts."
msgstr "这是多卡训练的已知问题。请确保使用最新版训练脚本。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:36 d695b207a9174d1e99f1544e33f59948
msgid "Output Quality Issues"
msgstr "输出质量问题"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:38 03940131830e4193a40882011d7e0b01
msgid ""
"**Model ignores input text after fine-tuning (overfitting):** (`#169 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/169>`_)"
msgstr ""
"**微调后模型忽略输入文本（过拟合）：** （`#169 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/169>`_）"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:41 8abeb0dd44d245f4a87dbc9f806cd045
msgid ""
"The model has overfit to reproducing training audio without text "
"conditioning. This is the most common fine-tuning failure mode and can "
"emerge surprisingly early (within a few hundred steps for small datasets)."
msgstr "模型过拟合为在无文本条件下复现训练音频。这是最常见的微调失败形态，且可能很早出现（小数据集几百步内即可发生）。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:43 eddbd9bf6a64482486534e771fff937c
msgid "Keep ``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` (do NOT set it to 0)."
msgstr "保持 ``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` （不要设为 0）。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:44 657415a5a72d4f1e866e99ea3c2af193
msgid "Keep ``weight_decay=0.01``."
msgstr "保持 ``weight_decay=0.01``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:45 5353c72f172f4b63ac678d9bc40c83a4
msgid "Reduce learning rate to ``1e-5`` (full FT) or ``1e-4`` (LoRA)."
msgstr "将学习率降至 ``1e-5`` （全量微调）或 `` 1e-4`` （LoRA）。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:46 118765609b4b458e978b7078f1533276
msgid ""
"Monitor checkpoints at each ``save_interval``. For most single-speaker "
"tasks, 1–3 epochs is sufficient — training beyond that often hurts."
msgstr ""
"在每个 ``save_interval`` 关注 checkpoint。多数单说话人任务 1–3 个 epoch 足够 — 继续训练往往适得其反。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:48 2440ff60da3b47ae941399e8a85386bc
msgid ""
"**Generation doesn't stop (runaway output):** (`#195 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/195>`_, `#124 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/124>`_)"
msgstr ""
"**生成停不下来（输出失控）：** （`#195 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/195>`_、`#124 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/124>`_）"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:51 8adb7595ebc34617b756b8703f0403ee
msgid ""
"Check your training data for clips with long trailing silence (>0.5 s) and "
"trim them — this is the most common cause."
msgstr "检查训练数据中是否存在尾静音过长（>0.5 s）的片段并裁掉 — 这是最常见原因。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:52 6e16c72bca834fdaae6a7cd917f88b86
msgid "Enable ``retry_badcase=True`` at inference time as a safety net."
msgstr "推理时启用 ``retry_badcase=True`` 作为兜底。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:53 526ec549999047bca487dd55c0319e42
msgid ""
"If fine-tuning a new language, the stop loss and diffusion loss may converge"
" at different rates — try increasing the stop loss weight (``lambdas > "
"loss/stop``)."
msgstr "若在做新语言微调，停止损失与扩散损失收敛速度可能不一致 — 可尝试提高停止损失权重（``lambdas > loss/stop``）。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:57 00277e2bd6964faeae68daadff8d18e3
msgid "LoRA Issues"
msgstr "LoRA 相关问题"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:59 759be0361fc2427ca58cc8f37feadf8a
msgid "**Poor LoRA quality:**"
msgstr "**LoRA 效果不好：**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:61 9f9ffa3f6ad840e48fdbe71495d815c3
msgid ""
"Increase ``r`` (LoRA rank) — try 32 or 64 for harder tasks like style or "
"language adaptation."
msgstr "增大 ``r`` （LoRA rank）— 风格或语言适配等更难任务可试 32 或 64。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:62 551220758aca4bf98304a3b1d10ba158
msgid "Adjust ``alpha`` — try ``alpha = r`` or ``alpha = 2*r``."
msgstr "调节 ``alpha`` — 可试 `` alpha = r`` 或 `` alpha = 2*r``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:63 c845b24252c64e81811475d0fa41dd0d
msgid "Ensure ``enable_dit: true`` — this is essential for voice quality."
msgstr "确保 ``enable_dit: true`` — 对音质至关重要。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:64 b38c1ad5a6f64a42bf87746352da3959
msgid "Increase training steps if the model has not converged yet."
msgstr "若尚未收敛，可适当增加训练步数。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:66 9b1da54bad23451189447bd0715bd0d7
msgid "**LoRA not taking effect at inference:**"
msgstr "**推理时 LoRA 未生效：**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:68 70fb28fb077a493d84754ba8a74fcdba
msgid ""
"Ensure the inference LoRA config (``r``, ``alpha``, ``enable_lm``, "
"``enable_dit``) matches the training config exactly."
msgstr ""
"确保推理侧 LoRA 配置（``r``、`` alpha``、`` enable_lm``、`` enable_dit``）与训练时完全一致。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:69 89426944c72145829a91e571ab6dd9a9
msgid ""
"Check the return value of ``load_lora`` — ``skipped_keys`` should be empty."
msgstr "检查 ``load_lora`` 的返回值 — `` skipped_keys`` 应为空。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:70 d7be562c6d394f9089c6876517eaf7d5
msgid ""
"Verify ``set_lora_enabled(True)`` is called if you previously disabled it."
msgstr "若曾关闭 LoRA，请确认已调用 ``set_lora_enabled(True)``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:74 a982abeebb3b424e9d2e246dee391400
msgid "Checkpoint Issues"
msgstr "Checkpoint 问题"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:76 7ef279b9001646e0a3a81148e25da66a
msgid "**Checkpoint loading errors:**"
msgstr "**Checkpoint 加载错误：**"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:78 564d5d7d871c41708aa9c76d6d6df500
msgid ""
"**Full fine-tuning:** the checkpoint directory must contain "
"``model.safetensors`` (or ``pytorch_model.bin``), ``config.json``, and "
"``audiovae.pth``."
msgstr ""
"**全量微调：** 目录须包含 ``model.safetensors`` （或 `` pytorch_model.bin``）、`` "
"config.json`` 与 `` audiovae.pth``。"

#: ../../finetuning/faq.rst:79 68102c3cdefc4a6a9af96affe91bbf62
msgid ""
"**LoRA:** the checkpoint directory must contain ``lora_weights.safetensors``"
" (or ``lora_weights.ckpt``) and ``lora_config.json``."
msgstr ""
"**LoRA：** 目录须包含 ``lora_weights.safetensors`` （或 `` lora_weights.ckpt``）与 `` "
"lora_config.json``。"
